'''赫羅斯葳塔'''（{{lang-la|Hrotsvitha Gandeshemensis}}，{{bd|约935||1001年|}}）是一位出生于[[巴特甘德斯海姆|巴特甘德斯海姆]]的[[撒克遜人|撒克逊]]贵族，她被认为是德国歷史上第一位女作家、第一位女詩人<ref name=":72">{{Cite journal|title=Hroswitha of Gandersheim. Her Life, Times and Works, and a Comprehensive Bibliography. Edited by Anne Lyon Haight|last=Bayerschmidt|first=Carl F.|date=1966-11-01|journal=The Germanic Review: Literature, Culture, Theory|issue=4|doi=10.1080/19306962.1966.11754646|volume=41|pages=302–303|issn=0016-8890}}</ref>、第一位女性历史学家和第一位戏剧創作家<ref name="name-doctor.com">{{Cite web|title=Hrotsvitha - Name's Meaning of Hrotsvitha|url=http://www.name-doctor.com/name-hrotsvitha-meaning-of-hrotsvitha-50282.html|accessdate=2019-12-03|work=Name-Doctor.com|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516143508/https://www.name-doctor.com/name-hrotsvitha-meaning-of-hrotsvitha-50282.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的戏剧和诗歌等作品主要在[[奥托王朝|奥托王朝]]時期用[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]創作<ref name="name-doctor.com" />。她的作品一度失傳，直到1501年被人文学者[[康拉德·策尔蒂斯|康拉德·策尔蒂斯]]重新發現<ref name=":28">{{Cite journal|title=Hroswitha of Gandersheim and the Destiny of Women|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_historian_1979-02_41_2/page/295|last=Frankforter|first=A. Daniel|date=February 1979|journal=The Historian|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1540-6563.1979.tb00548.x|volume=41|pages=295–314|issn=0018-2370}}</ref>。赫羅斯葳塔平時居住在[[甘德斯海姆修道院|甘德斯海姆修道院]]。<ref name=":08">{{Cite web|title=Hrotsvitha of Gandersheim – The Most Remarkable Women of her Time|url=http://scihi.org/hrotsvitha-gandersheim/|accessdate=2019-11-23|author=Sack|date=2019-02-06|first=Harald|work=SciHi Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417174212/http://scihi.org/hrotsvitha-gandersheim/|dead-url=no}}</ref>           

